DOC.brief_summary: This study is collecting serum and urine samples at various time points during pelvic floor physical therapy for women with pelvic pain.The biomarkers will be analyzed for cytokines and proteomics at various time points.
DOC.detailed_description: Collection points will be baseline, and at the last PT visit.
DOC.criteria: Women in the Beaumont Women's Urology Center who have pelvic pain and are starting pelvic floor PT in our center. all others
